<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About BlitzLaunchpad - Empowering Non-Technical Founders</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/images/fav_icon.png">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/script.js" defer></script>
    <style>
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
        .animate-float {
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .bg-blur {
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 via-indigo-900 to-purple-900 text-white">
    <%- include('../components/header') %>

    <main class="pt-24">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-purple-400 to-pink-400" data-aos="zoom-in">
                        Our Story
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-10 text-blue-100" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                        Empowering visionaries to build the future
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-30">
                <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-blue-500 rounded-full filter blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full filter blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Journey -->
        <section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400" data-aos="fade-down">
                    Our Journey
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-32">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0 md:pr-8">
                            <img src="./assets/images/the_spark.jpg" alt="The Spark" class="rounded-lg shadow-xl">
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-300">The Spark</h3>
                            <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
                                BlitzLaunchpad was born from a simple yet powerful idea: to empower non-technical founders to bring their visions to life. We recognized a gap in the startup ecosystem where brilliant ideas were left unrealized due to technical barriers. Our mission became clear - to bridge this gap and unleash the potential of visionary entrepreneurs.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0 md:pl-8">
                            <img src="./assets/images/the_launch.jpg" alt="The Launch" class="rounded-lg shadow-xl">
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-8">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-300">The Launch</h3>
                            <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
                                With our vision set, we assembled a dream team of startup veterans and tech experts. Each member brought unique insights and experiences from successful ventures and cutting-edge technologies. Together, we crafted a launchpad designed to turn innovative ideas into market-ready products with unprecedented speed and efficiency.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0 md:pr-8">
                            <img src="./assets/images/growth.jpg" alt="The Growth" class="rounded-lg shadow-xl">
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-300">The Growth</h3>
                            <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
                                As we helped more startups succeed, our expertise and services expanded to meet evolving needs. We refined our processes, embraced cutting-edge technologies, and deepened our understanding of various industries. This growth allowed us to offer more comprehensive support, from idea validation to scaling strategies, ensuring our clients' success at every stage of their journey.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0 md:pl-8">
                            <img src="./assets/images/future.jpg" alt="The Future" class="rounded-lg shadow-xl">
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-8">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-300">The Future</h3>
                            <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">
                                Today, BlitzLaunchpad stands at the forefront of startup innovation. We're not just building products; we're shaping the future of entrepreneurship. Our commitment to empowering non-technical founders remains stronger than ever, and we continue to push the boundaries of what's possible in startup development. With each success story, we're redefining the startup landscape and opening doors for the next generation of visionary entrepreneurs.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Approach -->
        <section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400" data-aos="fade-down">
                    Our Approach
                </h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg" data-aos="fade-up">
                        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-4xl text-yellow-400 mb-4"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Innovative Thinking</h3>
                        <p class="text-blue-100">We challenge conventional wisdom and explore creative solutions to complex problems.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                        <i class="fas fa-users text-4xl text-green-400 mb-4"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Collaborative Partnership</h3>
                        <p class="text-blue-100">We work closely with founders, becoming an extension of their team throughout the journey.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket text-4xl text-blue-400 mb-4"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Agile Execution</h3>
                        <p class="text-blue-100">We embrace rapid iteration and continuous improvement to deliver results quickly.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-4xl text-purple-400 mb-4"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Growth-Oriented</h3>
                        <p class="text-blue-100">We focus on scalable solutions that can grow with your startup's success.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Values -->
        <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 via-indigo-800 to-purple-800">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400" data-aos="fade-down">
                    Our Values
                </h2>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center">
                    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4 p-4" data-aos="zoom-in">
                        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg text-center h-full">
                            <i class="fas fa-star text-4xl text-yellow-400 mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Excellence</h3>
                            <p class="text-blue-100">We strive for the highest quality in everything we do.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4 p-4" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100">
                        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg text-center h-full">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake text-4xl text-green-400 mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Integrity</h3>
                            <p class="text-blue-100">We build trust through honesty and transparency.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4 p-4" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="200">
                        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg text-center h-full">
                            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-4xl text-blue-400 mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Innovation</h3>
                            <p class="text-blue-100">We embrace creativity and push boundaries.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4 p-4" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="300">
                        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-lg text-center h-full">
                            <i class="fas fa-users text-4xl text-purple-400 mb-4"></i>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Collaboration</h3>
                            <p class="text-blue-100">We believe in the power of teamwork and partnerships.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400" data-aos="fade-down">
            Join Us in Building the Next Generation of Startups
        </h2>
        <p class="text-2xl mb-10 text-blue-100" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            Ready to turn your vision into reality? Let's start your journey together.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
            <a href="#" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-purple-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full text-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
                Start Your Journey
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-blue-400 text-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-400 hover:text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full text-xl transition-all duration-300">
                Learn More
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-20">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-blue-500 rounded-full filter blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-1/3 h-1/3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full filter blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
</section>
</main>

<%- include('../components/footer') %>

<script>
AOS.init({
    duration: 1000,
    once: true,
    offset: 100
});
</script>
</body>
</html>